room_title: Escape room "Blitzkrieg" by Avalanche Escape Rooms in Anchorage
room_description: Players will join an Allied commando team tasked with stealing a mysterious artifact from a secret vault controlled by the mystical and enigmatic Brotherhood of the Black Sun. With challenges and puzzles inspired by the most ruthless military geniuses of WWII, this heart-pounding adventure developed by Labyrinth Portland will change the fate of millions!
